  "text": "The urine of each rat (20:00 pm-10:00 am) was collected every 3 days with dams housed individually in metabolic cages in the absence of food to eliminate contamination of urinary protein measurement by fallen food particles. Urinary protein level was measured using the pyrogallol red method [CITATION_1] .",
